I see us also having an R package that helps you work with brand YAML.

00:30:31.540 --> 00:30:37.859
And a very good fit for both of those would be a function that helps you pull brand YAML

00:30:37.859 --> 00:30:40.500
from a shared location into your project.

00:30:41.780 --> 00:30:44.819
I personally, if I were maintaining, like I said before, if I were maintaining a brand

